  <description>
    <p>
      AniDesk is an unofficial open-source desktop client for the Anixart mobile application,
      providing a convenient way to watch anime and get information about releases.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Use your Anixart account</li>
      <li>Built-in video player</li>
      <li>Video upscaling with Anime4K</li>
      <li>Discord Rich Presence</li>
      <li>Dark and light themes</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
